General.Name: ProfilGruppen AB (publ)
General.Description: ProfilGruppen AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, designs, develops, manufactures, and markets customized aluminum components and extrusions primarily in Europe. It serves furnishings, construction, electronics, and automotive industries. The company was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Åseda, Sweden.
